@startuml sequence-ai-logs
' =====================================================================
' Module 1 — AI LOGGING (ghi) + VIEWING (đọc)
' WRITE  : mọi lần gọi DeepSeek → aiLogger → DB (ai_matching_log) + file.
' READ   : GET /api/recommendations/logs → đọc ai-lab/logs/*.json
' Mục đích: theo dõi + cải thiện prompt (folder ai-lab/).
' =====================================================================
!theme plain
skinparam maxMessageSize 160
skinparam ArrowFontSize 11
autonumber

title Module 1 — AI Logging & Viewing\nGhi lại mọi lời gọi DeepSeek + xem lại để cải thiện prompt

actor "Ứng viên / Admin" as User
participant "deepseekClient" as DS
database "DeepSeek API" as AI <<external>>
participant "aiLogger\n(logAiCall)" as Logger
database "Supabase DB\n(ai_matching_log)" as DB
collections "ai-lab/logs/*.json" as File <<file>>
participant "AiLogsPage\n(Frontend)" as Page
participant "RecommendationController\n(getAiLogs)" as Ctrl

== GHI LOG (mỗi lần gọi AI — chạy ngầm trong finally) ==
User -> DS: (kích hoạt bất kỳ AI call nào:\nextract-cv / score)
DS -> AI: POST /chat/completions
AI --> DS: {content, usage{tokens}}
DS -> Logger: finally → logAiCall({task, model, prompt,\n  response, processingTimeMs, tokensIn/Out, success, error, metadata})

par Ghi song song 2 nơi
  Logger -> DB: INSERT INTO ai_matching_log\n(best-effort, không block nếu fail)
else
  Logger -> File: mkdir + writeFile ai_<ts>.json\n(timestamp + random id)
end

Logger --> DS: log entry (đã ghi xong)
DS --> User: trả kết quả AI

== XEM LOG (trang /ai-logs) ==
User -> Page: Mở trang "AI Logs"
Page -> Ctrl: GET /recommendations/logs?limit=50
Ctrl -> File: fs.readdir(LOGS_DIR)\n→ sort().reverse().slice(0, limit)
File --> Ctrl: danh sách file JSON gần nhất
loop Mỗi file
  Ctrl -> File: readFile + JSON.parse
  File --> Ctrl: log entry {task, prompt, response, tokens, ms, success}
end
Ctrl --> Page: 200 OK { logs[] }
Page --> User: Bảng log: task · model · tokens · thời gian ·\nthành công/thất bại (để phân tích + tinh chỉnh prompt)

@enduml
